{"tid":2421192,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★Drop！鄧聲興指提高印花稅影響深遠　北水或大減兩成！","createTime":"2021-02-24T10:46:49.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-24T21:16:48.000Z","uid":19454,"like":4,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"a588e3fb0110f82ddd9954f588a43d2406a4f60f","tid":2421192,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T10:46:49.000Z","msg":"香港股票分析師協會主席鄧聲興表示，提高印花稅稅率會增加交易成本，或會減少交易宗數，與現時全球主要市場減少股票印花稅稅率的大趨勢背道而馳，直言港府隨時得不償失。<br />\n <br />\n他續指，印花稅稅率增加的影響廣泛，對香港的國際金融中心地位也有影響，因港股市場有大量基金、北水、高頻交易參與，重視買賣成本。今次舉動可能令北水的流入規模減少10至20%，但相信不至於「散水」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20210224/bkn-20210224125237857-0224_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20210224%2Fbkn-20210224125237857-0224_00842_001.html&d=s5X1yiNR%2BigbIA3iGijs8Cukga04qSQtFIF%2FU0RrEoA%3D&h=08f349d3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20210224/bkn-20210224125237857-0224_00842_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"a408437115f0f4618746af8ca996562ec53aa543","tid":2421192,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T10:47:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13c79fa98a598c727db2ffcad5a97377186171c4","tid":2421192,"uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T10:47:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSHmmPBk.gif&amp;h=69c43eed&amp;s=540\" />"},{"pid":"bfe1a8ebc88d83f4bcd676f224abc581e08a1ae2","tid":2421192,"uid":321374,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T10:48:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmo